      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Happy to side with STYLIN' (7) here on the back of two impressive wins, the latest over 1100m at this track. She jumped a $1.95 favourite last time and was very impressive from the back of the pack. Faithfull remains in the irons and with her upside, she makes plenty of appeal. LAVISH CHARM (1) has now won four on-end, resuming with an all-the-way win over 1100m last time out. He was a $1.20 favourite there and this looks to shape beautifully for him once more. Nottle rides and he can extend his winning run. GIBRALTAR GOLD (3) won well here fresh before flying home over this track and trip last time out. The draw is a query, though she'll carry less weight today with Tsang's claim coming in handy. Won't be far away. DREAMERS NEVER DIE (2) can play a leading role on resumption from an inside draw. LADY NEGRONI (6) won't be far away if she can run up to her first-up effort.",
